s of the Lab\. + Build functional proofs of concept\. + PhD in a quantitative field and a minimum of 5 years experience working in complex computing and analytic contexts \(or equivalent experien **Qualifications** Requirements: + PhD in a quantitative field and a minimum of 5 years experience working in complex computing and analytic contexts \(or equivalent experience\)\. + Experience with modern data mining techniques and technologies e\.g\. information retrieval, text analytics, machine learning, natural language processing, speech technologies, model design, visualization, probabilistic models\. + Deep understanding of statistics and probability and evaluation techniques\. + Profound knowledge of working with data: data structures, data representation, data cleaning, data governance, and research database design\. Experience with educational data is a plus\. + Excellent understanding of, experience with and demonstrated success in modern scientific research methods\. **Primary Location:** US\-CO\-Centennial **Work Locations:** US\-CO\-Centennial\-2154 East Commons 2154 East Commons Avenue Centennial 80122 **Job:** Professional Development **Organization:** Global Product **Employee Status:** Regular Employee **Job Type:** Standard **Shift:** Day Job **Job Posting:** Jul 15, 2016